  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>Last updated: December 2025</p>

  <p>Stellar ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our application.</p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>TikTok account information (such as username, user ID)</li>
    <li>Public profile data and authorized content</li>
    <li>Basic technical data for authentication purposes</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To authenticate users via TikTok Login</li>
    <li>To provide and improve application features</li>
    <li>To comply with TikTok API policies</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>We do not sell or rent user data. Data is only shared when required to provide app functionality or comply with legal obligations.</p>

  <h2>Data Security</h2>
  <p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your data.</p>

  <h2>User Rights</h2>
  <p>You may request data deletion by contacting us.</p>

